Some simple scripts to download the latest browser nightlies

WINDOWS
To run Firefox nightly parallel to your normal install on your Windows machine you have to
- create a new profile for it              firefox -P
- start firefox with this profile using    firefox -p "<profile name>" -no-remote
- and start your standard firefox with     forefox -p "default" -no-remote

MAC
- do the same steps the apple way, the following link might help:
  http://weblogs.mozillazine.org/asa/archives/2008/08/shortcut_to_lau.html